706221f-b.text:
Park Street, between Broadway and Beaver Street, showing M. P. A. men working on a highway project. View 1 shows them removing the street car tracks, viewing eastward from Broadway along the north side of the street; view 2 is westward toward Broadway from Beaver Street and shoes the B. M. T. "E1" on the former.

View 1: September 25, 1935
View 2: October 21, 1935

Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
Credit Line Imperative
